title: DUSTY SPRINGFIELD - The Complete Studio Recordings 1961-1995+
description:
DUSTY SPRINGFIELD - The Complete Studio Recordings 1961-1995+

Codec: mp3.
Description: MPEG-1 Audio Layer 3.
Bit rate: VBR 192-320 kbps.
Sample rate: 44100 Hz joint stereo.
Tag types: ID3V2 & ID3V1.
Source formats: CD/DVD (see below).
Number of tracks: 643 (Recordings/mixes/remixes commercially released on CD and/or DVD as of April 2009. Digitally remastered stereo mixes unless otherwise noted).

Question: are you aware of the fact that Universal Music release at least one new compilation of Dusty Springfield's greatest hits every three months? Think about it for a second: one every three months. Over a period of ten years. Can you think of any other artist who has their greatest hits re-released every three months? Read: download, enjoy, share - and draw your own conclusions as to who benefits from the sales of all those compilations....
